videos.description: Alabama continues their dominance against unranked opponents as the Tide roll past Arkansas 41-9. Jalen Hurts had 196 total yards with one passing and one rushing touchdown in the Crimson Tide's victory over the Razorbacks.
videos.title: College Football: Alabama takes care of Arkansas

videos.description: No. 9 Ohio State rolls past Nebraska, 56-14. The Buckeyes scored on their first eight possessions and put up 50+ points for the 4th straight game, tying the school record.
videos.title: College Football: Ohio State beats Nebraska

videos.description: USC had to fight back after a slow start against Utah, but the Trojans powered back and stopped the Utes on a late 2-point conversion to seal a vital Pac-12 victory. Despite fumbling 3 times, Sam Darnold redeemed himself with 358 passing yards and 3 touchdowns on the day.
videos.title: College Football: USC holds off Utah
